title: Legendary Country Blues Guitarists - 2014 (DVD5)
description: Featuring Skip James, Bukka White, Son House, Rev. Gary Davis, Sam Chatmon, Big Bill Broonzy, Will Shade, Ralph Willis, Willie Trice, Blind Connie Williams and Henry Johnson. This DVD collection presents some of the rarest footage of legendary Country Blues artists that we havebeen fortunate to find. The footage varies from hi-quality film to analog videos taped over 40 years ago. But above all, the music and performances are powerful and evocative. The sounds of Skip James, Bukka White, Big Bill Broonzy, Son House, Will Shade, Rev. Gary Davis and others on this collection will give you shivers up your spine and get your feet tapping. This is the Country Blues of a time long past
